sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Staff (Desktop)
    participant Desktop as Desktop App
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as Database
    participant SignalR as SignalR Hub

    %% 1. Authentication Flow
    Note over User, DB: 1. Authentication Process
    User->>Desktop: Enter Credentials
    Desktop->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API->>DB: Validate User
    DB-->>API: User Valid
    API-->>Desktop: Return JWT Token & User Info
    Desktop->>SignalR: Connect to Hub (with Token)
    SignalR-->>Desktop: Connection Established

    %% 2. Order Creation Flow
    Note over User, DB: 2. Creating an Order
    User->>Desktop: Select Table & Add Items
    User->>Desktop: Click "Place Order"
    Desktop->>API: POST /api/orders
    API->>DB: Save Order & OrderItems
    DB-->>API: Saved Successfully
    API->>SignalR: Broadcast "OrderCreated" event
    SignalR-->>Desktop: Receive "OrderCreated"
    API-->>Desktop: Return OrderDetails

    %% 3. Payment Flow
    Note over User, DB: 3. Payment Process
    User->>Desktop: Click "Checkout"
    Desktop->>API: GET /api/payment-settings (for QR)
    API-->>Desktop: Return Bank Info
    Desktop->>User: Show QR Code
    User->>Desktop: Confirm Payment Received
    Desktop->>API: POST /api/orders/{id}/pay
    API->>DB: Update Order Status to "Paid"
    API->>DB: Release Table
    API->>SignalR: Broadcast "TableUpdated"
    SignalR-->>Desktop: Update Table Status (Green)
